      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to a bowl with your<strong> five-spice mix </strong>and <strong>cornflour</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the chicken is fully coated in the cornflour mixture – this is your <strong>five-spice coated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1655800111974-x200.jpg",
