      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, add it to the <strong>sticky glaze </strong>one piece at a time and turn to coat evenly – this is your <strong>sweet & sticky five-spice chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
