    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, fill the <strong>toasted brioche halves</strong> with the <strong>sweet & sticky five-spice chicken</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>sticky glaze </strong>and top with some of the<strong> tangy slaw</strong></p><p>Serve with the <strong>chips </strong>and <strong>remaining tangy slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
